title: Gifts from friend has vanished
body: my friend has sent me nocturne, eternum noturne, and a night hunter rengar... and they are all gone can someone explain me this?

replies.body:
Since this is an account-specific issue about content on your account, I recommend reaching out to our specialists in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new).

Le me know if you have any questions.
